# Protonmail
IMAPAccount proton
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User paulleehuang@protonmail.com
PassCmd "pass email/proton"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType STARTTLS
SSLVersion TLSv1.2
CertificateFile ~/.config/protonmail/cert.pem    

MaildirStore proton-local
Path ~/mail/Protonmail/
Inbox ~/mail/Protonmail/inbox/
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore proton-remote
Account proton

Channel proton
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
Patterns "*"
CopyArrivalDate yes
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# Gmail
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User paulleehuang@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass email/gmail"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/Gmail/INBOX/
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Trash"
CopyArrivalDate yes
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *